for the non raiding warrior</span><hr size=1> I think my armor is pretty good all around ( although if you can think of some reasonable upgrades please feel free ) The problem is I have a windblade but I HATE it, yes the damage is nice but I just cant stand using a 2 hander, way way too slow for my tastes. So my question is should I sell the windblade &amp; my 2 decent 1 handers ( frosty &amp; snowchipper ) &amp; get either....<br>
<br>
swiftblade of zek 11/18 10ac 10str 100hp 60kish <br>
<br>
horn of hasgra 13/20 35ac! 75hp 85kish<br>
<br>
fleshgrinder 12/19 75hp effect fireblast 65kish<br>
<br>
what combo of these or any other droppable 1 handers would you guys recommend? <br>
<br>
I really love the stats on the zek horn combo but will this combo be decent for taunt purposes in POP? Or would I be better off keeping the weapons I have &amp; spending my money elsewhere? <br>
<br>
btw I'm unguilded so no raids or main tank duties for me<br>
<br>
thnx <br>
<br>
Loops<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=538659">www.magelo.com/eq_view_pr...num=538659</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=viladdarorcslayer>Viladdar Orcslayer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/30/02 3:30:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4753.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: weapon help for the non raiding warrior</span><hr size=1> Suggestion 1 : DON'T sell the Windblade. You are not guilded, you are level 55, you will never be able to loot one till maybe lvl 62+ and with tons of luck. The drop rate of the Windblades have been nerfed to hell, so I expect the price on them to slowly go up. It is one of the best (if not the best) droppable 2 handers. The other weapons you mentionned will rather go cheaper and cheaper, the only fact that you see them on the market is a sign. Plus you actually CAN camp them, or will be able in a few levels. So, I'd suggest to not to sell the Winblade. Just wait to be lvl 60, you'll get triple attack and swing even more often with it. Plus your haste item is one of the good ones. You'll dish out crazy damage. Indeed.<br>
<br>
Suggestion 2 : you got tons of HP for a lvl 55. That's cool. But your str is only 101 (if your magelo is correct). That sucks. Try to get it to 150. You should notice the difference in the windblade damage. By the way, it might be one of the reasons that you are not satisfied with your windblade. Low str = low attack = way more misses. Try to fix your str. <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=170660" target="top"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:small;">Viladdar Orcslayer - Teir'Dal Warlord</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://kinesis.fr.st" target="top"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:small;">KINESIS</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=daminy7th>Daminy7th</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/30/02 6:38:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4753.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: weapon help for the non raiding warrior</span><hr size=1> My girlfriends warrior is 64 and she used to use the SBoZ/Horn combo for the stats. But when she got a Windblade at 63 the one handers have been bagged ever since. So I would hold on to the Windblade till 60 when ya get triple attack.<br>
