></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 1249<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/30/02 7:59:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4753.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Re</span><hr size=1> I would be forced to say that the weapon skill does matter even when in the offhand. <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:Times New roman;font-size:medium;"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=170513">Varaho Carnicero</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
