<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>  &quot;Do you know the secret of steel?&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kaylessa@thesteelwarrior>Kaylessa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/30/02 9:06:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4753.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Re</span><hr size=1> Screw the horn its a 1hP weapon and your skill is maxed at 240ish. Id stay with 2hs and 1hs weapons. just my 2cp... <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=536727"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.cox.net/amazonguild/sigs/kaylessa.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wudgurorm>Wudgurorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/30/02 10:19:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4753.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Re</span><hr size=1> Windblades are incredible weapons, you may be swinging slowly, but if you will take a look at your Damage Per second you will find out you are doing Lots more damage per second vs. using 2 1h weapons. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=shikariiapoccalypse>Shikarii Apoccalypse</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>All in the reflexes</BR>Guardian of the Bunker</BR>STEEL WARRIOR Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 2234<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/31/02 4:27:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4753.topic&index=9>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Re</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Loops:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->taunt purposes in POP<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Keep the frosty and snowchipper; but a BBoT or something else cheap if you need more taunt, and don't worry about the SBoZ/horn/etc.<br>
<br>
Taunt wise the frosty owns them all. And like the others have said; a few more levels you'll see why the windblade sells for what all those weapons go for <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://publish.hometown.aol.com/crushr85/myhomepage/max.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tiejinnie>Tiejinnie</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 156<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/1/03 9:39:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4753.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://homex.coolconnect.com/member3/Tiejinnie/images/Avatar.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Re</span><hr size=1> Always remember.<br>
<br>
Weapons are for DPS. Don't depend too much on your weapons for stats, cos you might find yourself unwilling to give them up at a later stage, cos you depend too much on your weapons for the stats.<br>
<br>
Sure, the 100hp/10ac on SBoZ and 10sta/35ac on HoHsagra is very tempting, but the DPS, while decent, doesn't generate enough DPS to really pull taunt/aggro on the mobs at L60+.<br>
<br>
At L55, it's good, so long as you do not become too dependant on them.<br>
<br>
Aggro-wise, the Frostbringer might just edge out the SBoZ, not in terms on dps, but on account of it's proc.<br>
<br>
At 65, i'm currently using Shortblade of Lightning, Primal until the primal procs, then switch to Windblade [i'm bidding my time and dkp for a sweet 1H or 2H weapon to come my way hehe].<br>
<br>
